story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_0200: You’re at a dead end, Team Plasma!
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_0500:
No matter what any of you do, I won’t allow you
to stop me!
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_1000:
That kind of teamwork is only possible if they trust
each other from the bottom of their hearts.
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_1100:
N, you also have important friends you can
depend on.
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_1300: No! This is the third time!
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_1400:
I can’t believe I keep getting thwarted by such
pitiful fools!
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_1900: Enjoy your moment of victory while it lasts.
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_2000:
N... The next time we meet, I imagine you’ll just
defy me yet again.
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_2100: You fail to understand your father’s ideals...
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_2200:
It saddens me that my own son would betray me
like this.
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_2400: I just wanted to be a family with you, Father.
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_2500:
But...if you continue to hurt my friends, who are
dear to me...
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_2600: Don’t expect me to hold back.
story_teamplasma_02_09000/2401_1001_2700: You have an unpleasant look in your eyes.
